    <item>
      <title>法国的目光对富人而不是公司征税，以帮助资助国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/france-eyes-taxes-on-rich-not-companies-to-help-fund-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府希望向富人征税，因为它寻求方法来提高国防支出，同时以激烈的赤字和更高的借贷成本搏斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/france-eyes-taxes-on-rich-not-companies-to-help-fund-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙同意将加泰罗尼亚的边界控制归结为分离主义者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/spain-agrees-to-cede-catalan-border-control-in-win-for-separatists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙总理佩德罗·桑切斯（Pedro Sanchez）同意将对边界的控制权移交给加泰罗尼亚的安全部队，这是该地区分离主义者的重大胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/spain-agrees-to-cede-catalan-border-control-in-win-for-separatists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂停了三家公司的原木和大豆进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-suspends-imports-of-us-logs-and-soybeans-from-three-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已经停止了来自美国三个实体的大豆进口，进一步加剧了世界两个最大经济体之间的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-suspends-imports-of-us-logs-and-soybeans-from-three-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普国家讲话在价格恐惧的情况下测试经济信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-speech-to-congress-economy-tariffs-ukraine-on-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的黄金时段地址周二晚上来自国会大厦山（Capitol Hill＆Mdash）被称为“美国梦的更新”的编年史；在第二任期初期，正处于关键时刻，当选他以应对通货膨胀和改善经济的选民开始权衡其议程的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-speech-to-congress-economy-tariffs-ukraine-on-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EIB提出扩大国防资金投资标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/eib-to-propose-expanding-investment-criteria-for-defense-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行将提议扩大其任务，包括专门用于军事使用的项目，此举将扩大其投资任务以包括更多的国防支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/eib-to-propose-expanding-investment-criteria-for-defense-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:20:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>XI离开门开放，以衡量的对特朗普的回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-imposes-tariffs-on-us-soybeans-and-other-farm-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个月的第二次中，中国对美国关税进行了报复，其有针对性的行动似乎经过了校准，以避免唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）发动全球贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-imposes-tariffs-on-us-soybeans-and-other-farm-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了卖山雀的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了他对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，并以全面的进口征税征收，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，这使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与Zelenskiy发生冲突后，暂停了对乌克兰的军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/trump-pauses-military-aid-to-ukraine-after-clash-with-zelenskiy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统下令对乌克兰的所有军事援助暂停，在椭圆形办公室爆炸后，乌克兰总统在乌克兰总统的爆炸之后，在他国家最重要的盟友的支持下，加剧了Volodymyr Zelenskiy的热量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/trump-pauses-military-aid-to-ukraine-after-clash-with-zelenskiy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 23:48:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙反对派社会主义者不会排除谴责动议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/portugal-s-opposition-socialists-won-t-rule-out-censure-motion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙最大的反对党表示，它不会排除提议对总理路易斯·黑山（Luis Montenegro）提出谴责动议的可能性，后者一直面临着有关与家族企业有关的潜在利益冲突的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/portugal-s-opposition-socialists-won-t-rule-out-censure-motion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:24:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
